VARIABLE NAME: lpov_nbh_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Fraction children who grew up in a given tract and end up living in a tract with a poverty rate of less than 10% (according to tract-level Census 2000 data) in adulthood. Tracts where children live as adults are defined as the tract of the last non-missing address observed on tax returns

VARIABLE NAME: two_par_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Fraction of children claimed by two people in the year they are linked to parents

VARIABLE NAME: has_dad_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Fraction of children who have a male claimer in the year they are linked to parents

VARIABLE NAME: has_mom_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Fraction of children who have a female claimer in the year they are linked to parents

VARIABLE NAME: jail_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Fraction incarcerated on April 1st, 2010 (where incarceration is defined as residing in a federal detention center, federal prison, state prison, local jail, residential correctional facility, military jail, or juvenile correctional facility)

VARIABLE NAME: kfr_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Mean percentile rank (relative to other children born in the same year) in the national distribution of household income (i.e. own earnings and spouse’s earnings) measured as mean earnings in 2014-2015 for the baseline sample

VARIABLE NAME: staytract_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Fraction of individuals who live in one of their childhood Census tracts in adulthood

VARIABLE NAME: staycz_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Fraction of children who live in one of their childhood commuting zones in adulthood

VARIABLE NAME: stayhome_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Fraction of children who live at the same address as their parents in 2015
VARIABLE NAME: working_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Fraction of children with positive W-2 earnings in 2015

VARIABLE NAME: kir_stycz_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Mean percentile rank (relative to other children born in the same year) in the national distribution of individual income (i.e. just own earnings) measured as mean earnings in 2014-2015 for the baseline sample, but restricted to children who live in one of their childhood commuting zones in adulthood

VARIABLE NAME: kfr_stycz_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Mean percentile rank (relative to other children born in the same year) in the national distribution of household income (i.e. own earnings and spouse’s earnings) measured as mean earnings in 2014-2015 for the baseline sample, but restricted to children who live in one of their childhood commuting zones in adulthood

VARIABLE NAME: spouse_rk_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for [outcome]_[race]_[gender]_mean Mean individual income rank in 2014-15 for the spouses of children who grew up in the given tract. Child’s spouse refers to the person they are married to in 2015
VARIABLE NAME: par_rank_white_pooled_mean_se - VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Estimated standard error for par_rank_[race]_[gender]_mean
